Every terror regime and legit country needs money.  Money to pay the workers, money to feed the troops, money for buying items on the black market, money for financing terror operations, money for bribing or influencing other countries like France and russia, money for any transaction that might be filtered to that swiss bank account.  Don't be so naive to think billions is chump change.  Even that slave worker in Iraq needs money to be spent on him for food, drink, and rags.<br>
<br>
